#: ../../P/pointy-hat.rst:5
msgid "pointy hat"
msgstr "pointy hat"

#: ../../P/pointy-hat.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../P/pointy-hat.rst:10
msgid ""
"Syn. :ref:`wizard-hat`\\. This synonym specifically refers to the wizards of"
" Unseen University in Terry Pratchett's *Discworld* series of humorous "
"fantasies; these books are extremely popular among hackers."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`wizard-hat`\\ と同義。この同義語は特に、Terry Pratchettのユーモラスなファンタジー *Discworld*"
" シリーズの見えざる大学の魔法使いを指す。これらの本はハッカーの間で非常に人気がある。"

#: ../../P/pointy-hat.rst:14
msgid ""
"[BSD hackers; common] Notional dunce cap handed to the original author of a "
"bug that's been corrected. Unlike the wizard had, this is often self-"
"assumed: \"Somebody please pass me the pointy hat. I fouled up the distfile "
"rather badly. This fixes it.\""
msgstr ""
"[BSDハッカー。一般的]訂正されたバグの元の作者に手渡される観念上のとんがり帽子。wizard "
"hatと違って、これはしばしば自ら被るものである。「誰かそのとんがり帽子をくれ。distfileをかなりひどくしくじってしまった。これで直る」"
